"продукт в корзину."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale.rst:92
msgid "Remove the previous product from the scale."
msgstr "Уберите предыдущий продукт с весов."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale.rst:None
msgid "weighing window"
msgstr "окно взвешивания"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale.rst:99
msgid ""
"Make sure the scale returns to `zero` before weighing a new product. If it "
"does not, the :guilabel:`Order` :icon:`fa-angle-double-right` button remains "
"unclickable until it is reset."
msgstr ""
"Убедитесь, что весы возвращаются к `zero` перед взвешиванием нового товара. "
