#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods.rst:70
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Delivery Payment` option links a payment method to online "
"orders placed through :doc:`Urban Piper <restaurant/urban_piper>`. Select "
"the appropriate :guilabel:`Delivery Provider` to associate with the payment "
