#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals.rst:55
msgid ""
"To process an order :ref:`payment <pos/use/sell>` using a :ref:`configured "
"terminal <pos/terminals/configuration>` in the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/"
"open-register>`, select the terminal's :doc:`payment method <../"
"payment_methods>` on the :guilabel:`Payment` screen, then follow the "
"instructions displayed on the terminal screen."
msgstr ""
"Для обработки :ref:`платежа <pos/use/sell>` по заказу с "
"использованием :ref:`настроенного терминала <pos/terminals/configuration>` "
"в :ref:`кассе POS <pos/use/open-register>` выберите :doc:`способ оплаты <../"
"payment_methods>` терминала на экране :guilabel:`Платеж`, затем следуйте "
"инструкциям, отображаемым на экране терминала."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals.rst:60
msgid ""
"Once the transaction is successful, the payment is automatically validated "
"in the POS register."
msgstr ""
"После успешной транзакции платеж автоматически подтверждается в кассе POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals.rst:63
msgid ""
"If a connection issue occurs between Odoo and the payment terminal, the "
"transaction is automatically canceled."
msgstr ""
"Если возникает проблема с подключением между Odoo и платежным терминалом, "
"транзакция автоматически отменяется."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals.rst:65
msgid ""
"You can also manually abort and validate the order by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Force done` in the POS register."
msgstr ""
"Вы также можете вручную прервать и подтвердить заказ, "
"нажав :guilabel:`Принудительно завершить` в кассе POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals.rst:67
msgid ""
"To cancel the payment request, click :guilabel:`Cancel` in the POS register."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы отменить запрос на оплату, нажмите :guilabel:`Отмена` в кассе POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/adyen.rst:3
msgid "Adyen"
msgstr "Adyen"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/adyen.rst:5
msgid ""
"Connecting an Adyen payment terminal to **Odoo Point of Sale** allows you to "
"offer customers a smooth payment experience while simplifying the work of "
"cashiers."
msgstr ""
"Подключение платежного терминала Adyen к **Odoo Point of Sale** позволяет "
"предложить клиентам удобный процесс оплаты, упрощая при этом работу кассиров."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/adyen.rst:9
msgid ""
"Adyen payment terminals do not require an :doc:`IoT Box </applications/"
"general/iot>`."
msgstr ""
"Платежные терминалы Adyen не требуют :doc:`IoT Box </applications/general/"
"iot>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/adyen.rst:10
msgid ""
"Adyen terminals can be used in many countries, but not worldwide. Check the "
"`list of countries supported by Adyen <https://docs.adyen.com/point-of-sale/"
"what-we-support/supported-languages/#supported-countries>`_."
