#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:3
msgid "QFPay"
msgstr "QFPay"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:5
msgid ""
"QFPay is a payment service that offers payment solutions through the `HaoJin "
"App <https://qfpay.global/products/merchant-app/>`_ for customer "
"transactions with a physical terminal."
msgstr ""
"QFPay — это платёжный сервис, предлагающий платёжные решения через "
"`приложение HaoJin <https://qfpay.global/products/merchant-app/>`_ для "
"транзакций клиентов с физическим терминалом."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:9
msgid ""
"QFPay payment terminals do not require an :doc:`IoT Box </applications/"
"general/iot>` to operate."
msgstr ""
"Платёжные терминалы QFPay не требуют :doc:`IoT Box </applications/general/"
"iot>` для работы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:11
msgid "QFPay terminals are exclusively for Hong Kong."
msgstr "Терминалы QFPay предназначены исключительно для Гонконга."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:16
msgid "QFPay configuration"
msgstr "Настройка QFPay"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:18
msgid "To configure a QFPay payment terminal, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Чтобы настроить платежный терминал QFPay, выполните следующие шаги:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:20
msgid ""
"Create a QFPay account on the `QFPay website <https://qfpay.global/products/"
"qfpay-pos-api/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Создайте учетную запись QFPay на `веб-сайте QFPay <https://qfpay.global/"
"products/qfpay-pos-api/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:21
msgid ""
"Request the activation of `Asynchronous Notifications <https://sdk.qfapi.com/"
"docs/common-api/asynchronous-notification/>`_ from QFPay."
msgstr ""
"Запросите активацию `асинхронных уведомлений <https://sdk.qfapi.com/docs/"
"common-api/asynchronous-notification/>`_ у QFPay."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:23
msgid ""
"Provide the Odoo server address to QFPay, followed by `/qfpay/notify`, and "
"copy the notification key provided by QFPay."
msgstr ""
"Предоставьте адрес сервера Odoo компании QFPay, добавив `/qfpay/notify`, и "
"скопируйте ключ уведомления, предоставленный QFPay."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:25
msgid ""
"Set up the QFPay terminal by connecting the HaoJin App to the QFPay account "
"as instructed by QFPay, then copy the terminal's IP address."
msgstr ""
"Настройте терминал QFPay, подключив приложение HaoJin к учетной записи QFPay "
"в соответствии с инструкциями QFPay, затем скопируйте IP-адрес терминала."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:27
msgid ""
"Request a self-signed certificate from QFPay linked to the terminal's IP "
"address, and import it into the POS machine."
msgstr ""
"Запросите самоподписанный сертификат у QFPay, привязанный к IP-адресу "
"терминала, и импортируйте его в POS-машину."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:29
msgid ""
"Generate a :guilabel:`POS-KEY` from the HaoJin App: go "
"to :menuselection:`Haojin App --> My --> Settings --> Pos Call Up Key --> "
"Reset Key`. Then, copy the generated :guilabel:`POS-KEY`."
msgstr ""
"Сгенерируйте :guilabel:`POS-KEY` из приложения HaoJin: перейдите "
"в :menuselection:`Приложение Haojin --> Мой профиль --> Настройки --> Ключ "
"вызова POS --> Сбросить ключ`. Затем скопируйте "
"сгенерированный :guilabel:`POS-KEY`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:33
msgid ""
"The **Asynchronous Notifications** are automated messages confirming "
"successful payments or refunds by QFPay."
msgstr ""
"**Асинхронные уведомления** — это автоматические сообщения, подтверждающие "
"успешные платежи или возвраты средств через QFPay."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:35
msgid ""
"Write the server address as follows: `https://yourdomain.odoo.com/qfpay/"
"notify`."
msgstr ""
"Укажите адрес сервера следующим образом: `https://yourdomain.odoo.com/qfpay/"
"notify`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:36
msgid ""
"If the terminal's IP address changes, update it in the :ref:`Odoo POS "
"settings <pos/use/settings>` and request a new self-signed certificate from "
"QFPay."
msgstr ""
"Если IP-адрес терминала изменится, обновите его в :ref:`настройках Odoo POS "
"<pos/use/settings>` и запросите новый самоподписанный сертификат от QFPay."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:38
msgid ""
"If a QFPay account already exists, contact `technical.support@qfpay.com` "
"with the merchant information and server address."
msgstr ""
"Если учетная запись QFPay уже существует, свяжитесь с "
"`technical.support@qfpay.com`, указав информацию о продавце и адрес сервера."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:42
msgid ""
"Alternatively, retrieve the POS-KEY from the `MMS (Merchant Management "
"System) portal <https://merchant.qfpay.global/>`_: go to :menuselection:`MMS "
"portal --> Settings --> Device Settings`."
msgstr ""
"В качестве альтернативы получите POS-KEY с `портала MMS (Система управления "
"продавцом) <https://merchant.qfpay.global/>`_: перейдите "
"в :menuselection:`Портал MMS --> Настройки --> Настройки устройства`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:51
msgid ""
