msgid ""
"Once you have added images to products or categories, configure their "
"visibility *in the POS register*. To do so, navigate to the :ref:`POS "
"settings <pos/use/settings>`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`POS interface` "
"section, and under :guilabel:`Hide pictures in POS`, enable/"
"disable :guilabel:`Show product images` and/or :guilabel:`Show category "
