#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:397
msgid ""
"Enable :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Invoice` to allow sending an "
"invoice to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Включите :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Счёт`, чтобы разрешить отправку "
"счёта клиенту."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:404
msgid "Receipt printing"
msgstr "Печать чека"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:406
msgid ""
"To allow receipt printing, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and enable :guilabel:`Early Receipt Printing` "
"under the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` section."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы разрешить печать чеков, перейдите в :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` и включите :guilabel:`Early Receipt Printing` в "
"разделе :guilabel:`Point of Sale`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:409
msgid ""
"After a successful :ref:`order payment <pos/restaurant/bills/payment>`, "
"click :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Print Full Receipt` to generate and print "
"a bill."
msgstr ""
"После успешной :ref:`оплаты заказа <pos/restaurant/bills/payment>` "
"нажмите :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Печать полного чека`, чтобы сформировать "
"и распечатать счёт."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:413
msgid ""
"If a printer is :doc:`configured and linked <hardware_network/"
"receipt_printers>` to a point of sale, the receipt is automatically printed "
"upon payment confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Если принтер :doc:`настроен и связан <hardware_network/receipt_printers>` с "
"точкой продаж, чек автоматически печатается при подтверждении оплаты."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:417
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:422
msgid "Tips"
msgstr "Советы"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:427
msgid ""
"To allow tipping in a POS, go to the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>`, "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Payment` section, enable :guilabel:`Tips`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы разрешить чаевые в POS, перейдите в :ref:`настройки POS <pos/use/"
"settings>`, прокрутите вниз до раздела :guilabel:`Оплата`, "
"включите :guilabel:`Чаевые` и нажмите :guilabel:`Сохранить`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:431
msgid ""
"Depending on your hardware setup and geographical location, enable the "
"following options as relevant:"
msgstr ""
"В зависимости от настройки оборудования и географического местоположения "
"включите следующие параметры по необходимости:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:434
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add tip through payment terminal (Adyen)`: Only works with "
"an :doc:`Adyen <payment_methods/terminals/adyen>` card terminal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Add tip through payment terminal (Adyen)`: работает только с "
"карточным терминалом :doc:`Adyen <payment_methods/terminals/adyen>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:436
msgid ""
":ref:`Add tip after payment <pos/restaurant/tips-after-payment>`: Only works "
"for a POS in the United States of America with an :doc:`Adyen "
"<payment_methods/terminals/adyen>` or a :doc:`Stripe <payment_methods/"
"terminals/stripe>` :ref:`payment terminal <pos/terminals/configuration>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Add tip after payment <pos/restaurant/tips-after-payment>`: работает "
"только для POS в США с :doc:`Adyen <payment_methods/terminals/adyen>` "
"или :doc:`Stripe <payment_methods/terminals/stripe>` :ref:`платежным "
"терминалом <pos/terminals/configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:442
msgid ""
"Saving the :guilabel:`Tips` setting automatically fills the :guilabel:`Tip "
"product` field with the preconfigured :guilabel:`[TIPS] Tips` product, which "
"is only used for tips. When selecting another product in the :guilabel:`Tip "
"product` field, the chosen product is no longer available on the :ref:`POS "
"register <pos/restaurant/orders>`."
msgstr ""
"Сохранение настройки :guilabel:`Tips` автоматически заполняет "
"поле :guilabel:`Tip product` предварительно настроенным "
"товаром :guilabel:`[TIPS] Tips`, который используется только для чаевых. При "
"выборе другого товара в поле :guilabel:`Tip product` выбранный товар больше "
"не доступен в :ref:`кассе POS <pos/restaurant/orders>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:446
msgid "Choose only one tip product per POS."
msgstr "Выберите только один продукт для чаевых на каждый POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:451
msgid "Tip and payment"
msgstr "Чаевые и оплата"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:453
msgid ""
"To process a tip during :ref:`payment <pos/restaurant/bills/payment>`, "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Чтобы обработать чаевые во время :ref:`оплаты <pos/restaurant/bills/"
"payment>`, выполните следующие действия:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:455
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-heart` :guilabel:`Tip`, add the amount, then "
"click :guilabel:`Ok`."
msgstr ""
"Нажмите :icon:`fa-heart` :guilabel:`Чаевые`, добавьте сумму, затем "
"нажмите :guilabel:`Ок`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:456
msgid ""
"Select a :doc:`payment method <payment_methods>` for the order and the tip."
msgstr "Выберите :doc:`способ оплаты <payment_methods>` для заказа и чаевых."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:460
msgid ""
"If the order and the tip are paid using different payment methods, select "
"a :doc:`payment method <payment_methods>` for the order first. Then, select "
"a payment method for the tip, click :icon:`fa-heart` :guilabel:`Tip`, add "
"the tip amount, and click :guilabel:`Ok`. Finally, :guilabel:`Validate` the "
"payment."
msgstr ""
"Если заказ и чаевые оплачиваются разными способами оплаты, сначала "
"выберите :doc:`способ оплаты <payment_methods>` для заказа. Затем выберите "
"способ оплаты для чаевых, нажмите :icon:`fa-heart` :guilabel:`Tip`, добавьте "
"сумму чаевых и нажмите :guilabel:`Ok`. Наконец, :guilabel:`Validate` платеж."

