"displayed on the preparation display."
msgstr ""
"Когда заказ принят, его :guilabel:`Статус заказа` переключается "
"с :guilabel:`Размещен` на :guilabel:`Подтвержден` и автоматически "
"отображается на экране подготовки."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:308
msgid "When the order is ready,"
msgstr "Когда заказ готов:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:310
msgid "Open the orders' list view."
msgstr "Откройте список заказов."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:311
msgid "Select the order."
msgstr "Выберите заказ."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:312
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Mark as ready` button. Its :guilabel:`Order Status` "
"switches from :guilabel:`Acknowledged` to :guilabel:`Food Ready`, and "
"its :guilabel:`Status` switches from :guilabel:`Ongoing` to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Нажмите кнопку :guilabel:`Отметить как готовый`. Его :guilabel:`Статус "
"заказа` переключается с :guilabel:`Подтвержден` на :guilabel:`Еда готова`, а "
"его :guilabel:`Статус` переключается с :guilabel:`В процессе` "
"на :guilabel:`Оплачен`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:317
msgid "Order rejection"
msgstr "Отклонение заказа"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:319
msgid ""
"Sometimes, the shop or restaurant may want to **reject** an order. In this "
"case, open the orders' list view,"
msgstr ""
