msgid ":ref:`Access the POS register <pos/use/open-register>` and make a sale."
msgstr ":ref:`Откройте кассу POS <pos/use/open-register>` и совершите продажу."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:81
